Their personality and character lie deep within their being.
I wanted to create an intimate atmosphere that would allow me to capture the personalities of the great flamenco figures with the help of the camera".
The Cante de las Minas Festival gave Bauer a boost in his long journey in 1997 to capture flamenco singers, guitarists and dancers with a disc-based camera.
These portraits, with their camera and subject matter, are reminiscent of classic photography.
