We can walk on the wall with super-strong glue.
Using super-strong glue to defy gravity and walk on walls like Spider-Man.
This is the goal set by several U.S. research centers, and a team of four institutions is close to achieving it.
With a piece of adhesive just one inch [2.5 cm] square, researchers were able to glue a 100-pound [100 kg] body to a vertical wall and hold it there.
